org.openftc.revextensions2

Interface VexMC29


  • @ServoType(flavor=CONTINUOUS,
           usPulseLower=1000.0,
           usPulseUpper=2000.0)
 @DeviceProperties(xmlTag="VexMC29",
                  name="VEX Motor Controller 29",
                  description="VEX Motor Controller 29",
                  compatibleControlSystems=REV_HUB)
public interface VexMC29
    Support for the VEX Motor Controller 29 To use an MC29, connect it to a servo port, then on the Robot Controller or Driver Station, configure the port you connected it to as a VEX Motor Controller 29
